  "text": "Here and thereafter, for \u2200P \u2208 K n \\{Q 0 } we denote \u2212 \u03b1 Q 0 ,j (D\u03bc (x 0 ,t 0,r ) ) \u2212 iU [CITATION_1] 0,j (x \u2212 x 0 ) \u2212 i U [CITATION_2] r,j (t r \u2212 t 0,r ).",
